OL,3,CPolice widows forced to choose between
OL,4,Clove and financial security
OL,6,FA police widow from Leicester is
OL,7,Fcalling on the Government to end what
OL,8,Fshe calls 'injustice' that means some
OL,9,Fwidows and widowers of police officers
OL,10,Fhave to choose between love and
OL,11,Ffinancial security.
OL,13,FUnder archaic rules, some police
OL,14,Fwidows in England and Wales can lose
OL,15,Ftheir partner's pensions if they
OL,16,Fremarry or cohabit with a new partner.
OL,18,FJo Bosworth, a former police officer
OL,19,Fherself, lost her husband Andrew to
OL,20,Fcancer not long after she retired from
OL,21,Fservice in 2005.
