OL,3,CPolice widows forced to choose between
OL,4,Clove and financial security
OL,6,FJo and Andrew served together at
OL,7,FLeicestershire Police and Andrew was
OL,8,Fdue to retire shortly after his wife.
OL,9,FHowever, he fell ill when the couple
OL,10,Fwere on holiday and he was later
OL,11,Fdiagnosed with terminal cancer.
OL,13,FAndrew was given three weeks to live
OL,14,Fand he died before reaching state
OL,15,Fpension age.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
