OL,3,CPolice widows forced to choose between
OL,4,Clove and financial security
OL,6,FFollowing her husband's death, Jo
OL,7,Freceived half of his police pension.
OL,8,FHowever, the rules of that time
OL,9,Fmaintain that if she was to take the
OL,10,Fnext step with someone new she could
OL,11,Flose that money.
OL,13,F"It would be a big thing for us to be
OL,14,Fable to say we got our pensions", said
OL,15,FJo. "We are being punished a little
OL,16,Fbit. My husband paid a lot of money
OL,17,Finto our pensions and people don't
OL,18,Frealise that. I think a lot of people
OL,19,Fthink we just get a pension but we
OL,20,Fpaid a significant amount of our wages"
