OL,6,F"I was married to my husband for 25
OL,7,Fyears before he passed away", she
OL,8,Fadded.
OL,10,FKate Hall was widowed at the age of
OL,11,F24, after her husband died in the line
OL,12,Fof duty when their daughter was just
OL,13,Ffour-years-old.
OL,15,FPC Colin Hall, a West Midlands Police
OL,16,Fdog handler, died in the line of duty
OL,17,Fafter he suffered a fatal heart attack
OL,18,Fwhen responding to an emergency call.
