OL,3,CPolice widows forced to choose between
OL,4,Clove and financial security
OL,6,FKate received her husbands pension,
OL,7,Fbut years later when she moved in with
OL,8,Fher new partner she lost it.
OL,10,FShe campaigned along with other police
OL,11,Fwidows and widowers for eight years
OL,12,Ffor changes to the 1987 pension
OL,13,Fregulations.
OL,15,FHowever, her campaign was met with
OL,16,Fseveral legal challenges, including
OL,17,Fthe Court of Appeal upholding a ruling
OL,18,Fwith prevents surviving partners of
OL,19,Fpolice officers in the scheme from
OL,20,Fkeeping their pension if they remarry
OL,21,For move in with someone else.
