OL,3,CPolice widows forced to choose between
OL,4,Clove and financial security
OL,6,FJo and Kate will join other police
OL,7,Fwidows on Wednesday as they attend a
OL,8,Fparliamentary event organised by the
OL,9,FNational Association of Retired Police
OL,10,FOfficers.
OL,12,FWidows in Northern Ireland and
OL,13,FScotland keep their pensions
OL,14,Fregardless of relationship status.
OL,15,FHowever, in England and Wales many who
OL,16,Fare part of pre-2006 schemes face
OL,17,Ffinancial loss if they decide to move
OL,18,Fon with someone new.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
