OL,3,CPolice widows forced to choose between
OL,4,Clove and financial security
OL,6,F"It is serious, it is not much fun",
OL,7,Fhe added.
OL,9,FA Home Office spokesperson told ITV
OL,10,FNews Central: "Pension provisions for
OL,11,Fpolice officers have evolved over
OL,12,Ftime. While the 1987 Police Pension
OL,13,FScheme included remarriage
OL,14,Frestrictions in line with other public
OL,15,Fsector schemes of that era, modern
OL,16,Fpolice pensions from 2006 and 2015
OL,17,Fdon't have these limitations.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
