OL,6,F"Retrospectively changing the 1987
OL,7,Fscheme, which was not originally
OL,8,Fcosted to provide these extended
OL,9,Fbenefits, would create additional
OL,10,Fcosts for current officers and
OL,11,Ftaxpayers - with wider implications
OL,12,Facross all public sector pensions."
